Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:09.07,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Non sexas tan amable comigo, \Nnon sei coma reaccionar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:12.32,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:12.32,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Con todas esas palabras amontoandose, non podo ver sequera á túa cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.87,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,mienaiyo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.87,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sequera podo ve-la túa cara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:31.59,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:31.59,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Onde está? Perdín a chave, agora non a atopo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:38.35,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki... surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:38.35,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspiro, queimareime se sigo actuando así sempre que fallamos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:44.98,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:44.98,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Estamos preto? Non o sei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:52.23,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:52.23,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Do lonxe que estás, \Nmesmo se estás xusto aquí
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:59.37,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:59.37,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Non sexas tan amable, ves? \NFacémonos dano un ó outro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:06.21,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso demo ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:06.21,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Con tódalas mentiras\Namontonandose, non podo moverme
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:13.63,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:13.63,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Quero verche agora, pero non sei que dicir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:23.85,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kurai kimi ni ha egao misetai
