Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:40.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio es ti, Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que raro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que ben atoparte aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si... que coincidencia...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alguén que coñeces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A súa mellor amiga, aparentemente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero por que estás aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oín que estabas tomando o día libre do traballo porque estabas ocupada co equipo de atletismo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Ben... eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Queres que {\i1}eu{\i0} lidie con isto??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ola!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, é Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poida que estedes os dous nunha cita?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, algo así.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Espera, que—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E por que estás ti aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estamos facendo unha sesión de fotos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agora mesmo estou nun descanso.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, Aragaki—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Simplemente podes chamarme Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ayase-chan entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agora temos un pouco de présa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino? Sénteste ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás bastante calada, e pareces estresada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Si, Estou un pouco por baixo do tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que tal se alguén te leva de volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:46.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Levareiche as bolsas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grazas, pero estou ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoa por interrumpi-la túa cita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:04.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa sabes, estiven preguntandomo, pero coñeces a esa xente que está atrás de túa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se non bulimos, perderémolo anime das 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoade rapazas... grazas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que pasou con esas dúas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vense en serio estrañas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quen sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non coñezo a esas frikis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe, estaba a pasar algo hoxe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Foi probablemente á Comiket de Verán.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Comiket de Verán?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que é iso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:46.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu non estou segura, pero venden doujinshi e outras cousas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Doujinshi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ela non ten esperanza...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás agochando algo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro que non!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoa, collerémoste noutra ocasión!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deica, Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Espera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que escapas, Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non estou escapando...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:10.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mentira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás mintindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mentiras, mentiras, mentiras, mentiras! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non me mintas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Intentabas escapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás fuxindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás escapando!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase? Isto—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cala, Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou falando con Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:36.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino, estou preocupada por ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que por favor respondeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estás agochando algo, non?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non o estou, Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non estou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa deberías sabelo agora, Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Odio as mentiras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non mo vas dicir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non queres falar comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:05:00.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou abraiada. E pensei que eramos amigas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Parece que malentendin as cousas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Síntoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:12.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quero axudarche, Kirino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Algo parece mal hoxe, e non podo deixarte marchar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que hai na bolsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mercado de circulos de Comic"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onde vas? Non rematei de falar—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Síntoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa non podo sela túa amiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por favor, xa non me fales na escola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non coñezo a esas frikis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:18.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non creo que a señorita Kiririn estivese falando en serio aló atrás.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Os humanos son uns animais moi desafortunados.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grazas polo de antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grazas a ti, conseguimos facelo dalgún xeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdón por usarvos así.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Intentei chamar á señorita Kiririn tamén, pero non me respondeu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estaba bastante cansa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa fora á cama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio? É bo escoitalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A señorita Kuroneko tamén estaba bastante preocupada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sentímolo de novo por iso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Farei que se desculpe con ela tamén.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non te preocupes por iso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moitas grazas polo de hoxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chao entón.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dao o todo no campamento de adestramento!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quen cres que son, Mamá?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Marcho entón!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:30.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cando usa os seus tentáculos, o lombo de Reika queda ao descuberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Non me malinterpretes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é coma se te buscara isto nin nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nas súas marcas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:54.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:56.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gañaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agora podes loitar contra outros xogadores!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estou de volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:37.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agora podo usa-la miña personaxe contra outros xogadores.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh si?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fai moito tempo que non facemos isto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Facer que?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:09:00.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabes, volver á casa xuntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro, somos maiores agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesmo durante o verán só andabamos á biblioteca ou ó parque.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é iso...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non o entendes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:15.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que, Kyou-chan, que che está preocupando ultimamente?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que queres dicir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non che preocupa nada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non en realidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero falaches do consello vital de Kirino...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, así que é iso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Qu-Que?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdón, Manabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Teño que sacar algo do meu peito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Estudaremos xuntos doutra vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boa sorte, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.07,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnI hate Comic Sans\1c&H3629AE&\bord0\shad0\be1\fs30\b1\frz12.073\pos(706,271)}New term
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pasouche algo na escola hoxe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non en realidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase incumpriu a súa promesa e contou a todos sobre a túa afección?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase non faría iso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Reconciliácheste con ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira para aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Se non dis nada, non podo axudar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cala!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que demo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:18.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Falo contigo un pouquiño e agora estás actuando lexeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E que ten de malo iso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non me importa se son lexeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:31.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Despois de todo, son un imán siscon idiota pervertido que pensa que ten algo bo despois de coñecer un pouco á súa irmá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non vou deixar que marches de aquí ata que me conte toda a historia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Qu-Que pasa contigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non te reconciliaches con Ayase, non?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Como podería?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Despois do que pasou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pero actuaches coma se nada pasara o día seguinte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:52.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiña campamento de adestramento, así que non podía decepcionar a ninguén.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que se supón que significa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:11:03.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moita xente quería ir ó campamento, e como me escolleron para ir, non podía quedarme deprimida e non traballar duro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:06.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ese era un problema aparte, e no campamento tiven que centrarme en face-lo que tiña que facer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa vexo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que non intentaches chamala ou algo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que cres que estás facendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é coma que puidera evitalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é a túa mellor amiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,En serio vas deixa-las cousas así?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ti—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cala!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deixa de falar coma se souberas o que estou pasando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:26.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Déixame soa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:30.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non podo atura-la forma en que simplemente estás renunciando así!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non es ti!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:37.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Normalmente tratarías de arranxalo como puideses, por moi mal que se vexa ou baixas que fosen as probabilidades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que actuas todo maduro de súpeto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recibir unha charla de ti despois de tanto tempo realmente me anoxa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perdoa, pero non vou sentarme a escoitar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:50.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non vou simplemente asentir e facer o que dis, como fai a veciñiña.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:51.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Por que ti—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non me toques!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:58.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nunca te preocupaches por min en toda a miña vida, e só agora estás intentando interpretar o papel do irmán maior?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que acabas de...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cala!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro que non podo deixalo así!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Xa o sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Espera—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non coma min?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Intentar arranxalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non o digas coma se fora tan sinxelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non entendes bocado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Só non o entendes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non o entendes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O consello vital non acabou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:33.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma a responsibilidade ata o final!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Só di iso dende o principio a próxima vez, parva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Debo negarme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non podo relacionarme con alguén con ese tipo de afección.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:44.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oe—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Déixame preguntarme en vez diso.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que pensas dela?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Porén, a resposta é obvia neste punto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, espera—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,É todo a túa culpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino non é ese tipo de persoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dixen que esperes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Escoitame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que lle dixeches hoxe a Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Foi un esforzo inútil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Era á súa mellor amiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:12.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non é natural que quixese reconciliarme con ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Si...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Así que lle dixen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:20.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deixa esa afección e bótao todo".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabe-lo que dixo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ela díxome, "Nunca!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isto significa que a súa afección é máis importante para ela ca min!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Que crúel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:38.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non trato de defende-la súa afección, pero non entendes moi ben que tipo de hobby é, non?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Decidiches que o odias sen saber nada diso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vino no telexornal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:50.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Os xogos e animes nos que a xente fai cousas lascivas ás nenas están cada vez máis estendidos en Xapón.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deu a nova un famoso xornalista.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non son ese o tipo de cousas que ten Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, supoño que o son...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:07.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Entón, cando descubro que a miña mellor amiga ten unha afección tan noxenta, non é natural que intente facela parar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ese xornalista tamén dixo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:15.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As persoas que xogan e miran esas cousas acabarán por tolear da cabeza e perde-la súa humanidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iso é unha esaxeración.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:22.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,E había un home que se viu influenciado por aqueles xogos para electrocutar a unha nena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:31.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O culpable era un deses chamados otakus aspirantes a criminais, e dixo que estaba tentando imitar o que viu nun xogo chamado "Siscalypse".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non o viches?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:37.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Non se debería permitir que existan este tipo de xogos e mangas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:34.97,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H454545&\bord0\shad0\fs60\b1\pos(813,500)}SisCa{\1a&HFF&}ly incident
